@0 = ~You'd better talk to my husband if you want to find out what's going on around here.~
@1 = ~You must be travelers, right? When I was young, I wanted to be a traveler so badly.~ 
@2 = ~My sister should have arrived from Luskan a few days ago. I hope she'll be here soon.~ 
@3 = ~I'd give you a couple cooking lessons, but tramps like you don't stay in one place long.~ 
@4 = ~Oh! You frightened me. I'm not used to meeting strangers, because traveling is dangerous these days.~ 
@5 = ~I hope the weather turns soon. Without a good harvest, we'll have a hard time.~ 
@6 = ~I like the look of you, but my husband's coming over soon, so I'm sorry.~ 
